Sprinkled throughout any tutorial are implications that the presented paradigm will not bear weight. That your idea, fully realized, will quickly overflow the container of &ldquo;hello world&rdquo;. Tutorials always have the scent of primary school, preparing you for a life that doesn&rsquo;t exist.
Before the structure collapses, or before building ensues ask:
&ldquo;Is my project small or big?&rdquo;
